@WeatherApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5144

### Get all weather records from database
GET {{WeatherApi_HostAddress}}/api/weather
Accept: application/json

###

### Get weather by ID
GET {{WeatherApi_HostAddress}}/api/weather/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get weather by coordinates (will check database first, then API if needed)
GET {{WeatherApi_HostAddress}}/api/weather/coordinates?latitude=51.5074&longitude=-0.1278
Accept: application/json

###

### Get weather for New York coordinates
GET {{WeatherApi_HostAddress}}/api/weather/coordinates?latitude=40.7128&longitude=-74.0060
Accept: application/json

###

### Get weather for Tokyo coordinates  
GET {{WeatherApi_HostAddress}}/api/weather/coordinates?latitude=35.6762&longitude=139.6503
Accept: application/json